Question - Update Table Name 
Answer - 
	RENAME TABLE old_table_name TO new_table_name; ( MySql, SQL Server)
	ALTER TABLE old_table_name RENAME TO new_table_name; ( ORACLE using alter)
	

Question - Update Column name and datatype in a Table 
Answer - 
	In MySQL
	
	--This will change datatype not column name
	ALTER TABLE table_name
	MODIFY COLUMN old_column_name new_datatype;
	
	-- to rename the column in table
	ALTER TABLE table_name
	CHANGE COLUMN old_column_name new_column_name current_datatype;
	
	--To rename column and change datatype
	ALTER TABLE table_name
	CHANGE COLUMN old_column_name new_column_name new_datatype;
	
	In Oracle
	
	-- Rename column
	ALTER TABLE table_name
	RENAME COLUMN old_column_name TO new_column_name;
	
	-- Change datatype
	ALTER TABLE table_name
	MODIFY (column_name new_datatype);
	
	